This method should set the additional options on top of the current options object._The current options object may contain pre-defined options based on flags that have_been configured on the state backend.__

It is important to set the options on the current object and return the result from_the setter methods, otherwise the pre-defined options may get lost.__@param currentOptions The options object with the pre-defined options._@return The options object on which the additional options are set.
